docs.snippet: MONTEVIDEO, Uruguay, April 9--Rear Admiral George J. Dufek and a group of United States Navy officers visited the Soviet whaling factory ship Slava today and were treated as if they were long lost brothers.

docs.snippet: BEAUMONT, Tex., April 14 (UP)--Louise Suggs, the leading money-winner on the women's pro golf tour, today took first place with 145 at the end of thirty-six holes in the $5,000 Babe Zaharias open golf tournament.
